<HEAD>With PM-Columbia-Sony, Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are the 10 largest acquisitions by dollar amount by
Japanese interests of major stakes or controlling interests in U.S.
companies, according to figures compiled by IDD Information
Services and The Associated Press.
   Listed are the U.S. company, the acquiring company, the dollar
amount and the date completed.
