Sony Corp., announced Sept. 27, 1989, pending.
   2. Firestone Tire &amp; Rubber Co., $2.65 billion by Bridgestone
Corp., May 5, 1988.
   3. Inter Continental Hotels, $2.27 billion by Seibu Saison, Dec.
15, 1988.
