by Paloma Co., September 1988.
   8. Union Bank, $750 million by California First Bank, June 30,
1988.
   9. LyphoMed Inc., $666 million by Fujisawa Pharmaceutical Co.,
announced Aug. 21, 1989, still pending.
   10. Reichhold Chemicals Inc., $549.7 million by Dainippon Ink &amp;
Chemicals Inc., Sept. 28, 1987.
